{"ChunkNum": 2, "StartTime": 432.1, "EndTime": 476.672, "Content": "|58|: Sometimes there's a song. |59|: If you're wearing green today, please stand up. |60|:  There's definitely reading of picture books and usually there's a theme. |61|: Maybe it's numbers, maybe it's letters, maybe it's colors to help little ones just get used to talking, reading, singing, playing, all of those early literacy skills that will help them with reading in the future. |62|:  One of our mottos is the library welcomes everyone. |63|: We really encourage all families, all students of any background to come to the library to take advantage of our resources. |64|: They are by the city, for the city.", "Embedding": [-0.00036199365, -0.022093074, -0.021056242, 0.038404718, -0.001672729, 0.021695806, 0.06575522, -0.044071626, -0.0032009524, -0.07181656, 0.01604712, -0.0034755506, 0.0016543383, -0.001711557, -0.024166241, -0.021675393, -0.016821947, -0.016140504, -0.010503226, 0.0011634615, 0.0029798544, -0.017209297, 0.060593918, -0.016280528, 0.029312406, -0.07935062, -0.017149234, 0.01205125, 0.038489833, -0.04953215, -0.033442233, -0.018730085, -0.02220559, -0.032786034, -0.00067138317, 0.021089576, 0.0034932462, -0.0018474383, -0.007839086, -0.014495065, -0.0074924123, -0.016226232, 0.010396827, 0.02259367, 0.007540492, -0.011076494, 0.011092648, 0.04761298, -0.006249035, 0.0020010907, 0.010162027, 0.0016738536, -0.031285826, -0.0074520484, -0.035776272, 0.031144543, 0.03225928, -0.013526635, 0.037230395, 0.039576504, -0.00080756185, 0.008081391, 0.016450685, -0.015427076, 0.00040908437, -0.014883246, 0.014349608, -0.013032341, 0.0066992943, -0.005284166, 0.02325892, 0.04357284, -0.0043751136, -0.004251992, -0.019639801, -0.0110006295, 0.0009326972, -0.008918689, -0.008025605, 0.010422431, -0.009495815, 0.023564296, -0.00026124337, 0.03272284, 0.0023103198, 0.026196659, 0.030720755, -0.0036742517, -0.047790818, 0.013040578, 0.020803783, 0.000922358, 0.0050798575, 0.018163912, 0.0027106667