{"ChunkNum": 7, "StartTime": 1412.671, "EndTime": 1588.109, "Content": "|197|:  in this week's Things to Do. |198|: Get to Central Avenue for the Jazz Festival, head to San Pedro for its Festival of the Arts, and pull some strings for Puppets in the Park at Hollyhock House. |199|: All this up next on Things to Do. |200|:  Thousands of toes will be tapping throughout the day on Saturday, September 20th. |201|: Celebrating its 30th year with four pavilions and three stages of live music, it's the Central Avenue Jazz Festival. |202|: The festival is presented by council member Curren Price and pays tribute to jazz greats while also shining a spotlight on emerging artists. |203|:  Enjoy hot, cool, and swinging jazz sounds with over a dozen performances taking place along Central Avenue from MLK Boulevard to Vernon Avenue. |204|: Central Avenue Jazz Festival is on Saturday, September 20th from 11 a.m. to 7 p.m. For more details, visit centralavjazzfest.com. |205|:  On September 20th, Los Angeles choreographers and dancers present the San Pedro Festival of the Arts in the heart of the harbor. |206|: Enjoy performances from 19 vibrant dance companies to mark the 19th year of the festival. |207|: There'll also be interactive performances and free family fun. |208|: Bring a picnic and get set to join in. |209|: Try a Bollywood step or a flamenco turn or simply enjoy the mix of dance performances by local companies. |210|:  Head to the Upper Green at Peck Park for the San Pedro Festival of the Arts on Saturday, September 20th, beginning at 1 p.m. For more details, visit tryartsp.com. |211|:  Bring a blanket, sing along, and make art at Puppets in the Park. |212|: Puppets in the Park is presented by the Department of Cultural Affairs and the Bob Barker Marionette Theater. |213|: On Sunday, September 21st, enjoy two performances of Fiesta. |214|: There will also be art activities led by Barnsdahl Junior Art Center instructors. |215|: Gates open at 9 a.m. Each performance will be followed by art activities. |216|: It's all happening on the West Lawn outside Hollyhock House. |217|:  Head to Barnes Doll Park for Puppets in the Park on Sunday, September 21st with performances at 9.30 a.m. and 11 a.m. For more information, visit hollyhockhouse.org. |218|: And that's a look at some things to do. |219|:  And that's all for this week. |220|: I'm Susan Huckle, and from all of us here at LA This Week, thank you so much for joining us. |221|: Remember that you can watch us online anytime at lacityview.org. |222|: We're also on Instagram, Facebook, X, and YouTube.", "Embedding": [-0.00028515744, -0.01234727, -0.051192418, 0.010476856, -0.0012526299, -0.018570587, 0.06612119, -0.026998108, 0.012815319, -0.012650098, 0.03886238, 0.02859984, -0.0021858888, 0.012230895, -0.0015471835, -0.014326282, -0.02519353, -0.044404652, 0.0021591678, -0.0059919828, 0.0019667405, -0.017478537, 0.023976816, 0.020727836, 0.052747272, -0.034875084, -0.019107575, 0.037513383, -0.05192628, -0.0028594178, -0.07602727, -0.0055634365, 0.030316066, -0.014855296, 0.0007195769, -0.0031696786, 0.016294137, 0.0064989245, -0.027191998, 0.0020797623, -0.043843832, 0.010649997, 0.033111464, -0.0020270422, 0.04883607, 0.001225044, 0.008587622, 0.015123205, -0.022944253, -0.0113162715, -0.0008752181, 0.0039553703, -0.01404469, -0.011015496, -0.022488717, 0.018684264, 0.0026518174, -0.00665469, -0.0014507965, -0.054645553, 0.009280257, -0.017490717, 0.019841403, -0.005262883, 0.00055320654, -0.0035403154, 0.005423929, -0.010941546, 0.00642517, -0.023509204, -0.0053092614, 0.0126462, 0.019242313, -0.016341206, 0.012813778, -0.011803325, -0.015135179, 0.0074504456, 0.004435941, 0.013809357, 0.023154862, 0.0052182125, 0.0010663198, 0.016664159, -0.022092659, 0.013719039, 0.023547962, -0.015666822, -0.005390321, -0.005596157, 0.017705176, -0.05723423, 0.018834872, -0.006539545, 0.0102566155, 0.011884777, -0.0041617407, -0.014575146, -0.004962131, 0.011707532, -0.016096065, -0.037213128, -0