{"ChunkNum": 12, "StartTime": 2880.62, "EndTime": 2959.497, "Content": "|298|: That is amazing. |299|: I love that. |300|: I'm 71 years old and every time I see them it's like, you know, my heroes. |301|: They're amazing. |302|:  Mostly the people say my DNA. |303|: And they're looking for activity to do something. |304|: Now, they can't play regular soccer because of the physical limitations. |305|: So this is the place that we offer them. |306|:  This is medicine for you guys. |307|: You know, think about, instead of going to your doctor, or sitting and complaining, or eating manches at the TV, you can come out, enjoy the sun, social, and walking soccer, and you have the competitive, the energy game, that Dermaline is running. |308|: So all this, it's really medicine. |309|:  The sense of community they have, it's really quite wonderful. |310|: I think so many older people are having trouble finding things to do in community and this is a really active way for them to do things. |311|: I think a lot of senior activities that are offered tend to assume\n|312|:  that the senior community is sedentary already, but there's quite a few people that want to move, they want to play, they want to continue to be active and it helps their psychology, it helps their physiology. |313|: We're really excited about the program and what it's done for the players.", "Embedding": [-0.0005268823, 0.045046795, -0.032791737, -0.042151306, -0.0020041922, 0.05759921, 0.05336372, 0.035216574, -0.010659452, -0.03577682, 0.039587986, 0.040762693, 0.0014562967, 0.01093151, -0.011392737, 0.0037719547, -0.020337492, -0.0020744374, -0.023250967, 0.00057078846, -0.0048851673, -0.007644454, 0.013415089, -0.012506393, 0.030887129, -0.07310106, -0.026952062, 0.0063349768, -0.002417035, 0.026796984, -0.03339903, -0.015122514, -0.010910805, -0.012603268, -0.0033923576, 0.01024731, 0.013231681, -0.0013563744, 0.005094829, -0.01697102, 0.002789874, 0.028407807, -0.0010310045, 0.0136553245, 0.0060899067