{"ChunkNum": 18, "StartTime": 3381.995, "EndTime": 3428.595, "Content": "|395|: It's true. |396|:  So I had no idea this program existed in the city of LA. |397|: And it is making me think about my retirement and where I'm going to be spending my time. |398|: And so Jeremy, thank you so much for leading on this. |399|: Ben, thank you for your vision. |400|: And it is very true. |401|: All the things you said right now are absolutely true. |402|:  As folks get older, you can't go shoulder to shoulder. |403|: You can't fight for that ball anymore, because it could be very serious injury. |404|: So the fact that you're having so much joy in something that you love, I think it's a wonderful example. |405|: It's great leadership for the City of LA. |406|: And Ben, you have my support. |407|: I do want to see this citywide. |408|: I think it's a great idea. |409|: But again, thank you for bringing this in and demonstrating an alternative way of doing things. |410|: And so thank you so much, Council Member Blumenfield.", "Embedding": [-0.00075302913, 0.0051545277, 0.011466372, 0.0063200817, -0.0033961576, 0.0647048, 0.06408466, 0.036245145, -0.011110941, -0.055777654, 0.023311524, 0.016301885, 0.0027601751, 0.03869081, 0.0056854454, -0.0038463084, -0.012632777, 0.023177778, -0.00025693094, 0.00097548484, -0.00025255137, 0.004959744, 0.0668532, 0.015141994, 0.03300585, -0.03536371, -0.031327393, -0.04241651, -0.020441616, 0.025248965, -0.060702264, -0.041634265, -0.011465593, -0.022834847, 0.0010500522, 0.024209207, 0.008356361, -4.7358506e-05, -0.012488951, 0.0017788148, -0.0117578115, 0.013957878, 0.018234957, 0.0059168003, -0.016017826, 0.017213156, 0.0052955355, 0.012431632, -0.011447208, -0.018418927, 0.0058916374, 0.0010732353, -0.0011270201, -0.024317762, -0.030345663, 0.06261245, 0.009467969, -0.00499397, 0.017021526, -0.012785111, 0.012223432, -0.012769662, -0.012778096, -0.022191929, -0.008545732, -0.032746796, -0.0057822284, -0.033288985, -0.0091809025, -0.010685