{"ChunkNum": 19, "StartTime": 3429.571, "EndTime": 3486.46, "Content": "|411|:  Thank you very much. |412|: I just want to invite the city councils to have a team or watch us on Lanark Park on Friday, 9 o'clock. |413|: All right. |414|: We'd have to move the whole council meeting there. |415|: But you know, field trip is always a good idea. |416|: Thank you very much. |417|: You guys are an inspiration. |418|: Thank you. |419|: Thank you so much. |420|: Another big round of applause. |421|: Mr. Nazarian, I'm sorry. |422|: You're on the queue. |423|:  Hold on, you don't want to miss this, guys. |424|: You don't want to miss this. |425|: All I just wanted to say is thank you very much, Councilmember Blumenfield. |426|: I'm echoing the sentiments of my colleague, but the funny thing is I'm 52, so there's hope, and I'm looking forward to joining all of you. |427|: And I just wanted to say for the record, football is God. |428|: So thank you for what you're doing. |429|: All right.", "Embedding": [-0.0005581348, -0.01226599, 0.018415522, 0.00606082, -0.0022560111, 0.053428654, 0.08457763, -0.023370082, 0.001487987, -0.06675965, 0.031928245, -0.008017538, 0.003773109, 0.055240486, 0.010811745, -0.0063626105, 0.008761669, 0.016696127, -0.0073436755, -0.00038410208, -0.00085584604, 0.0008652576, 0.04465302, -0.005662036, 0.038411763, -0.007143082, -0.029296037, -0.020050706, -0.025402322, 0.028029798, -0.09358001, -0.05292051, 0.01077295, -0.015774556, 9.71688e-06, 0.020400079, -0.0035157537, 0.0064993645, -0.03359708, -0.035556503, 0.0026086417, -0.007626737, 0.021229375, 0.001547818, 0.023575462, 0.011359792, 0.009319498, 0.054774955, -0.012534143, -0.038220856, 0.008643501, 0.00982134, -0.05719838, -0.008315323, 0.01376615, 0.012772523, 0.026149144, -0.0019309914, 0.008575388, -0.0021199817, 0.013269957, -0.004098589, -0.0054642917, -0.017599644, -0.012449522, -0.02368995, 0.0053015845, -0.021654818, 0.005628293, -0.0151924575, -0.0018177829, -0.010370767, 0.009940975, -