{"ChunkNum": 47, "StartTime": 7643.984, "EndTime": 7686.376, "Content": "|1099|:  And right now we're in a moment where it's back around where I think the world looks at you and others and says, yeah, this is what he's been talking about the entire time. |1100|: When racism goes from being dog whistle to just being whistle, which is what it is now, just straight up anti-Latino sentiment,\n|1101|:  unashamed, unembarrassed, immoral, and out front. |1102|: And you've been an opponent of that when it's subtle, but also when it's direct. |1103|: So thank you so much for everything that you've done, and we're proud to be able to honor you. |1104|: And with that, Councilmember Anandas. |1105|:  Mr. President, we have one more person to bring up.", "Embedding": [-0.00073329214, 0.039155643, 0.04939285, 0.0028069615, -0.0032158413, 0.038067482, 0.004230192, -0.0006707819, -0.0074859047, -0.010656607, 0.04471957, 0.026648121, 0.006118641, -0.00877946, 0.028923703, 0.011348023, 0.0019938163, 0.008822549, 0.004110329, 0.0005124526, -0.0098445285, 0.0376453, 0.09936339, 0.035211816, 0.07083298, 0.021838704, -0.024140988, -0.014289904, 0.022237055, -0.0073479507, -0.0070638545, -0.06180677, -0.030583829, -0.006682924, -0.0013067817, 0.00624327, 0.016767932, -0.0043548048, 0.011852445, -0.018629126, 0.00758312, -0.0073044626, -0.0028710635, -0.0054062665, 0.012557015, 0.010196696, -0.0035976707, 0.013923068, -0.019831158, -0.01364416, 0.011590382, 0.013845448, -0.0148082655, -0.015985588, -0.0522932, 0.027712584, 0.028989652, -0.0041882265, 0.050095208, -0.047335673, 0.013828409, 0.0040617217, -0.008853918, -0.022068663, -0.010791174, -0.02911145, 0.0007235043, 0.028120954, 0.0041577383, -0.013105581, -0.03519296, 0.014694249, 0.00045291672, 0.000100393096, 0.024071587, -0.01295136, -0.0075624343, 0.018409172, -0.020040678, 0.0053224536, 0.019025095, 0.0046510636, -0.009369124, -0.0140892705, -0.0022151053, -0.012531461, 0.031404816, -0.0016903112, -0.023547446, -0.00681624, 0.01