{"ChunkNum": 50, "StartTime": 8299.305, "EndTime": 8352.968, "Content": "|1194|: Good morning, Councilwoman Gerardo and members of the council. |1195|: My name is Carmella Liggins and I am here on behalf of my friends, House Foundation, which has faithfully served the Skid Row community every Wednesday for the past 16 years at 540 South San Pedro Street. |1196|: I am asking today for something simple but\n|1197|:  Vital weekly parking and loading permit on Wednesdays from 11 to 2 p.m. |1198|: The permit would allow our volunteers to unload full clothing shoes Housing resources and other essentials for me the request is deeply personal my daughter suffers from mental health Challenges and her known area of homelessness is the skid row community she knows and I know that every Wednesday between 11 and 2 she can find me and\n|1199|:  And she can find the volunteers of My Friends House Foundation. |1200|: So we're just asking for a weekly parking permit so that we can continue to service the community like we have been for the last 16, 17 years. |1201|: Thank you, Carmela Liggins.", "Embedding": [-0.00037406533, -0.004061596, -0.019144796, -0.020164842, -0.0015854326, 0.058248192, 0.04618756, 0.026585022, 0.010474122, -0.031873394, -0.04263314, 0.011910861, 0.0012323529, 0.0076113287, -0.014467879, 0.0048331576, -0.0135657415, -0.017636295, -0.020838613, -0.002174547, -0.006076601, -0.010077066, 0.10242491, -0.041156437, 0.028111361, -0.033504684, -0.026493326, 0.024016842, 0.023857035, -0.021636972, -0.08992038, -0.021581406, -0.042020995, 0.014869309, -0.00040740558, 0.0019805746, -0.0010361035, -0.005828745, 0.006053638, -0.0146792075, -0.0015092364, 0.034947626, -0.002271829, -0.0008523442, 0.01792781, 0.008380601, -0.0012253494, 0.034498636, 0.0042869193, -0.0063730334, 0.011965797, 0.008357311, -0.019673223, -0.015580603, -0.013616146, 0.008970752, 0.016066978, -0.004065196, 0.003918385, -0.029355168, 0.0020635063, -0.014627504, 0.00927957, -0.00663009, -0.0028122