{"ChunkNum": 54, "StartTime": 8365.373, "EndTime": 8447.212, "Content": "|1208|:  Good morning. |1209|: My name is Marvelous, and I am also with this young lady, Carmilla, out here to advocate for the parking situation that has been going on for the past 17 years this October. |1210|: We come out one day a week for three hours, and we've been harassed, we've been ticketed, everything but. |1211|: And we're looking for some kind of an answer to maybe having a pass\n|1212|:  to have us out there for those three hours. |1213|: It's been overwhelming. |1214|: The tickets are like $100. |1215|: The foundation, My Friend's House, which is what I'm wearing, again, has been out there 17 years this year. |1216|: And we serve the homeless with food, clothes, shoes, and our love. |1217|: And we're out there every Wednesday, rain or shine. |1218|: And I don't understand why we can't get some type of help where we can\n|1219|:  Load, offload, just have our volunteers come out and serve the community. |1220|: I'm sorry, ma'am, before you go, what's the addresses of the places that you're concerned about? |1221|: 540 South San Pedro. |1222|: Okay, thank you. |1223|: And it's called the bin. |1224|: Got it. |1225|: That we serve at. |1226|: We know the bin on 5th and San Pedro. |1227|: Got it, thank you.", "Embedding": [-0.00034401545, 0.0070237457, -0.023882842, -0.0305703, -0.0013533941, 0.037860494, 0.056673165, 0.023431294, 0.010241152, -0.051194802, -0.035511438, 0.017563708, 0.0053584115, -0.0066182003, -0.012788421, 0.03522177, -0.023239229, -0.03436745, 0.01777708, -0.0015568846, -0.008188589, 0.028871885, 0.09006691, -0.05219938, 0.06056395, -0.02370232, -0.03229168, 0.04578257, 0.026540032, -0.030281227, -0.09818178, -0.016879292, -0.022539657, -0.0046052067, -0.00057632825, 0.0034406502, -0.009946405, -0.006654399, 0.031369273, -0.026388474, -0.003728466, 0.008756869, 0.0016120184, 0.0020292392, 0.019987464, 0.017942907, -0.0034635467, 0.047798518, 0.008531407, -0.018727