{"ChunkNum": 71, "StartTime": 9456.118, "EndTime": 9512.267, "Content": "President. |1452|: Members, Team Price is excited to kick off the countdown to the 30th Annual Central Avenue Jazz Festival with a special community preview that's happening this weekend at Vermont Square Park. |1453|: It's going to be the place to be on Saturday the 14th for an afternoon of live music, great food, and family fun. |1454|:  Performances will feature the Neighborhood Orchestra, the Top Brass Shelf Band, bringing the spirit of jazz to South LA ahead of this year's big celebration. |1455|: Local vendors, Bootsy Barbecue, Gruegos, and others are going to serve with flavors alongside free food, kids' activities, and the community resources for the neighbors. |1456|: So plan on being there. |1457|: And then on the 20th,\n|1458|:  Please join us for the 30th anniversary of the Central Avenue Jazz Festival, up and down Central Avenue from Vernon to King Boulevard, music, fun, food, and celebration. |1459|: So everyone is welcome.", "Embedding": [-0.00038727795, -0.012236071, -0.00019401647, 0.029994596, -0.0014168113, -0.0026371162, 0.06349819, 0.0063625164, 0.00958702, 0.0006118091, 0.04128675, 0.040694688, -0.0037683167, 0.021259055, 0.0011628155, 0.0046340316, -0.027280679, -0.030373663, -0.010606953, -0.0061472, -0.00054347457, 0.0070260544, 0.05568252, 0.022033129, 0.022443125, -0.019779336, -0.025068123, 0.034088463, -0.06454801, -0.012341411, -0.08724804, -0.023180597, 0.017843006, -0.029177388, -0.00029036799, -0.0016918271, 0.0063424935, 0.004118701, -0.019278292, -0.01656699, -0.032236744, 0.014862309, 0.0134803625, -0.0046960763, 0.05317702, 0.0010501298, 0.011250119, 0.0017391767, -0.048354793, -0.0052591427, -0.0016551687, -0.0020235418, -0.025135593, -0.009619169, -0.01268458, 0.009431023, 0.026120983, -0.0056812554, -0.015197892, -0.0051242225, 0.009759507, 0.017634276, 0.0013897493, -0.0028061133, 0.0031577745, -0.0029906866, -0.007437232, -0.008849472, 0.0033650824, -0.