{"ChunkNum": 76, "StartTime": 9817.252, "EndTime": 9857.604, "Content": "|1500|: I just wanted to thank Mr. Nazarian for bringing this forward and really everybody who's up there, especially John Ardalan who is a constituent and a friend and really was the one who first brought this idea to me last year to recognize Masa Amini Day and it just spiraled from there with events in the park and\n|1501|:  Obviously, the movement, as was mentioned, is so important now more than ever, not just to spark that spirit of resistance in Iran, but here in this country, we need to be motivated and inspired by Masa Amini. |1502|: So thank you for bringing this forward.", "Embedding": [-0.00040412217, 0.04669332, 0.021999182, 0.019000493, -0.001837542, 0.07765411, 0.006263551, 0.038851824, 0.0064388085, -0.027031112, 0.02858897, -0.0267608, 0.0063413708, 0.0009383707, 0.03744709, -0.027474819, -0.055957038, -0.021426823, 0.008733198, 0.0012687267, -0.0064214338, 0.020353654, 0.07538355, 0.019723482, 0.04400536, -0.030364158, -0.03175732, -0.017079186, 0.025958838, 0.024841364, -0.035212614, -0.031374574, -0.000331166, 0.0041895355, 0.0038654257, -0.010144667, -0.011667579, -0.0044504786, -0.0090721585, 0.04272756, -0.001902941, -0.039983828, -0.018480023, 0.012294866, -0.014390093, -0.024694448, 0.0032147556, 0.031253748, -0.009994294, -0.02735049, 0.007794601, 0.0009500469, -0.044598076, -0.017429708, -0.043808874, 0.031584583, 0.006662097, -0.0026129037, 0.020031285, -0.0030172158, 0.019446893, 0.008455625, -0.032174725, -0.026837947, -0.0074332645, -0.017170765, -0.004997997, -0.012079133, -0.006181114, -0.0022564984, -0.024979813, 0.009344368, -0.003575917, -0.03389159, 0.0031561258, -0.02295957, -0.008258667, 0.009230908, 0.02217391, -0.004446706, 0.0063033304, 0.005629803, -0.014651057, 0.011236229, -0.003533857, -0.022890147, 0.020999862, -0.0024025498, 0.0021521575, -0.02470843, 0.005109128, -0.040243357, -0.0068848794, 0.023839608, -0.017067753, 0.017451152, 0.014662743, -0.